posts.post_title: T206 CB SGC 70 to trade for E94 Young
posts.post_content:
Hoping to see if any T206 collectors have an E94 Young to trade. I have cash to make up the difference if your card is worth more than mine. I'm not looking to sell, just hopefully acquire a tough E94 I need. 

Of the 494 CBs on the combined SGC/PSA population report, there are ten at this level and five above it (four 6's and a 7).
Nice card Steven, tougher common too....
